FBIS3-6357 "dreas052_c_94012" FBIS-EAS-94-052 Document Type:Daily Report 16 Mar 1994 North Korea Koreans in Canada Group Issues Statement SK1703023094 Pyongyang KCNA in English 2157 GMT 16 Mar 94 SK1703023094 Pyongyang KCNA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Pyongyang, March 16 (KCNA) -- The regional headquarters of Koreans in Canada of the National Alliance for the Country's Reunification (Pomminnyon) in a recent statement urged the United States to immediately withdraw the nuclear weapons of its forces in South Korea and solve the "nuclear issue" through dialogue with the DPRK. The statement demanded that the United States no longer obstruct the denuclearization of the Korean peninsula and the realization of the nation's desire to peacefully reunify the country divided into North and South.
